<section class="py-16 px-[5%]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold font-sans leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        Designer of Webz.<br>
        Maker of Thingz.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Two Column Layout: Paragraphs and Images -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
      <!-- Left Column: Text Content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-normalLight dark:text-invertedLight leading-tight mb-4">
          If you're starting wonder "who is this guy?"—I don't blame you. I've been asking myself the same question for
          years.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-normal dark:text-inverted mb-6">
          I'm a husband and father who loves technology and design. Remote work has been my default setting way before
          2020. Like before it was even called remote work. Before Zoom had their IPO. It was <i>my</i> thing before it
          became <i>our</i> thing.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-normal dark:text-inverted mb-6">
          Over the past 7 years, I've had the pleasure of collaborating with clients from 11 different countries—ranging
          from pre-seed startups to enterprise clients with billions in revenue.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-normal dark:text-inverted mb-8">
          You can learn more trivial facts about me by visiting the about page. Or skip directly to the case studies
          below.
        </p>

        {% render 'partials/text-link', url: '/about', label: 'Learn more about this guy' %}
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Image Grid Animation -->
      {% render 'partials/pixel-image-cycle', id: 'home-about-grid', images: null %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
